column20: 6/4 Telepathique, 5/2 Paggane, 7/2 Speculatrix, 5/1 Apple Away, 33/1 Shighness
column36: Very much a stayer but travels strongly and could be competitive over this far
column37: Classy mare but very much a stayer having won last season's 3m4f Grand National Trial at Haydock (good to soft; kept on) in February, after which she disappointed in the Midlands National; does travel strongly so unwise to dismiss purely on the strength of today's trip, especially on a stiff track; returns with yard in form.

column4: pricedup.bet Houghton Mares' Chase (Listed Race) (GBB Race)
column20: 6/4 Telepathique, 5/2 Paggane, 7/2 Speculatrix, 5/1 Apple Away, 33/1 Shighness
column36: Form figures of 11211 over fences, the latest a 2m4f Listed race; big shout on these terms
column37: First season over fences could barely have gone much better with four wins from five starts, latterly in a 2m4f Listed event at Huntingdon (good to soft) which she won despite jumping out to her left throughout (previous wins were on left-handed tracks); every chance on these terms if resuming where she left off; goes from the front.

column4: pricedup.bet Houghton Mares' Chase (Listed Race) (GBB Race)
column20: 6/4 Telepathique, 5/2 Paggane, 7/2 Speculatrix, 5/1 Apple Away, 33/1 Shighness
column36: Has something to find at these weights but with no fitness issues she's respected
column37: Has won two of her four chases and quite readily floored the odds-on favourite in a Listed novice at Chepstow three weeks ago (2m3f, good to firm; handles good but softer has looked troublesome); has something to find at these weights but with no fitness issues she's respected.

column4: pricedup.bet Houghton Mares' Chase (Listed Race) (GBB Race)
column20: 6/4 Telepathique, 5/2 Paggane, 7/2 Speculatrix, 5/1 Apple Away, 33/1 Shighness
column32: J Carthy, Mrs P Shanahan & R Bartlett
column36: Stayed further for Willie Mullins but recent second over hurdles came over this far
column37: All her improvement for Willie Mullins came over longer trips and she very nearly won last season's Killarney National over 3m2f; however, after two respectable Flat runs for this yard, she returned to jumps with a near miss over a similar trip to today's in Chepstow's always-competitive Silver Trophy Handicap Hurdle; clearly retains significant ability.

column4: pricedup.bet Houghton Mares' Chase (Listed Race) (GBB Race)
column20: 6/4 Telepathique, 5/2 Paggane, 7/2 Speculatrix, 5/1 Apple Away, 33/1 Shighness
column36: Strong stayer; very opposable at this trip and on these unfavourable terms

column4: Stephex Trucks UK Castletown Handicap Hurdle (GBB Race)

column4: Stephex Trucks UK Castletown Handicap Hurdle (GBB Race)
column20: 5/1 Personal Ambition,  Nurse Susan,  Florida Dreams,  Kapal Layar, 6/1 Siog Geal, 8/1 Dedicated Hero,  Hartington, 10/1 Karafon, 14/1 Nells Son, 20/1 Faivoir, 33/1 Jericoacoara
